collections.name: Mr.Soldier
collections.description:
AMr. Soldier: A Dream Reimagined

As a child, I dreamed of becoming a soldier and brought that dream to life through my drawings of Mr. Soldier. But life took me on a different path—I moved to a new country, built a family, and became a professional badminton coach.

Though I couldn't become a soldier, my dream never faded. Instead, I transformed it into art, creating Mr. Soldier as an NFT to share my journey. Not every dream comes true as we imagine, but they guide us toward success in unexpected ways. Dreams don’t die—they evolve.

collections.name: They Who Were Marked
collections.description:
Rhaezen – The Dark Purpose of Rhaezen
An NFT collection of 777 marked souls, harvested for a purpose beyond time.

They are not fallen. They are not lost. They have been chosen.

Rhaezen the Forsaken is not merely a warrior consumed by chaos—he is a harvester. He does not simply kill; he marks. Those who cross his path are not all slain—some are taken, their essence rewritten by the touch of Delimenor.

The Rhaezen are the forsaken, the claimed, the ones who no longer belong to Ilmeris or its fragile reality. Each of them was once something else—an Elphir warrior, a guardian beast, a scholar of balance. Now, they are fragments of a plan far beyond mortal understanding.

They do not serve. They are the mission.

Each Rhaezen carries the sigils of the Mark of the Forsaken, coordinates not of space, but of a future yet to unfold. Their weapons no longer strike merely to kill, but to weave something new into existence—an existence in which Ilmeris itself may have no place.
